      <div><strong style="color:#1a1a18;">Ash shovel and small brush</strong><br/><span style="font-size:.95rem;color:#5a5a54;">A dedicated ash shovel and brush set keeps the mess contained. Don't use your household dustpan — ash gets everywhere.</span></div>
